{"tid":2282473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"YouTube大當機 畫面圈圈跑不停","createTime":"2020-11-12T01:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T02:45:17.000Z","uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bc5b21d0645d77974f40836639014d5015352c9c","tid":2282473,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T01:32:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">YouTube大當機 畫面圈圈跑不停</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2020/11/12 08:51<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕今天上午8時許PTT「八卦板」網友發文詢問「YouTube是不是掛了」，稱打開影片跑不動，都是黑畫面。<br />\n<br />\n許多網友紛紛留言影片跑不出來，或是要等超久才能看，也有人在美國的網友回覆「美國掛了+1」，另外有人說「手機的打不開，但是電腦可以」。記者在8時40分用電腦實測，同樣卡在黑畫面，影片跑不動，YouTube臉書上各國網友也紛紛反映當機狀況。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">大約於8時50分，電腦實測YouTube恢復正常，但於9時10分實測，又出現當機狀況，YouTube臉書上有不少國家的網友反映尚未修好。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/3349373\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F3349373&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Au4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=f8b46ec6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F3349373&h=2c958d0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/3349373</a>"},{"pid":"73412d4b9e3564802e283f1525f790f53c878c14","tid":2282473,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T01:35:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">YouTube 全球大當機 原因不明</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n11 月 12 日，影音串流網站 YouTube 被多名網友舉報大當機，例如影片無法順利播放、無法順利開啟 YouTube Studio、無法直播等等。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">0858 更新：YouTube 表示正在努力搶修中</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/saydigi-tech.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/48f32bf03bb28dce77d01e70132099a2.jpg?w=1000&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fsaydigi-tech.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F48f32bf03bb28dce77d01e70132099a2.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26ssl%3D1&h=7399e711&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">根據回報網站《DownDetector》資訊，上午 7 點 44 分便開始有人舉報，範圍遍布全球。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://saydigi-tech.com/2020/11/32281.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsaydigi-tech.com%2F2020%2F11%2F32281.html&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Au4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=0520a5b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://saydigi-tech.com/2020/11/32281.html</a>"},{"pid":"301cf12faadd6abcf5ecc0a08a59cc35091c9722","tid":2282473,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T01:37:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">YouTube當機官方修復中 大量用戶影片「發生錯誤」</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2020/11/12 09:22<br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者吳家豪台北12日電）影音平台YouTube今天傳出當機，用戶觀看影片時，持續出現載入中的轉圈圈畫面，無法順利收看；YouTube團隊表示，已得知這項問題，並正在修復中。<br />\n<br />\n追蹤網路連線狀態的獨立網站DownDetector顯示，YouTube從今天上午約7時47分開始有大量用戶回報問題，其中96%為無法收看影片，另有2%發現網站相關問題、1%上傳影片時出狀況。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">DownDetector資料顯示，YouTube當機區域以北美為主，歐洲的英國、法國也有不少用戶回報問題，亞洲以日本災情較嚴重。</span><br />\n<br />\n記者向Google查證此事，尚未取得回覆，目前無法得知異常原因及影響範圍。（編輯：黃國倫）1091112<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202011125002.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202011125002.aspx&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Au4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=411b9a62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202011125002.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"28304d2e6dfef2bcb9ed93288015eec7130c7d16","tid":2282473,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T01:39:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">YouTube大當機全球哀號 圈圈狂轉1小時</span></strong><br />\n中廣新聞網<br />\n<br />\n2020年11月12日 上午9:05<br />\n留言<br />\n影音平台YouTube今(12)日一早約8點出現大當機，大批網友紛紛在各熱門節目留言區哀號「一片黑」、「不停轉圈圈」，時間長達1小時。<br />\n<br />\n不只台灣如此，許多在澳洲、美國的網友也上網崩潰抱怨什麼都看不到，即使順利登入，也時不時斷線再度無限轉圈圈。<br />\n<br />\n針對一早的異常狀態，目前YouTube還沒有做出說明，原因暫時不明。"},{"pid":"b8436769160e67a733d3839424824365a8003505","tid":2282473,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T01:42:51.000Z","msg":"Nov 11, 2020 4:33pm PT<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">YouTube Experiences Widespread Technical Problems Playing Videos</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://variety.com/2020/digital/news/youtube-down-widespread-video-problems-1234829639/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2020%2Fdigital%2Fnews%2Fyoutube-down-widespread-video-problems-1234829639%2F&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Au4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=0aea7d18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://variety.com/2020/digital/news/youtube-down-widespread-video-problems-1234829639/</a>"},{"pid":"1e01683325dc16a42e1cdd70255713b77dc757df","tid":2282473,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T01:45:02.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">YouTube down: Users report widespread problems</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mywabashvalley.com/news/national-news/youtube-down-users-report-widespread-problems/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mywabashvalley.com%2Fnews%2Fnational-news%2Fyoutube-down-users-report-widespread-problems%2F&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Au4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=878cd452\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mywabashvalley.com/news/national-news/youtube-down-users-report-widespread-problems/</a>"},{"pid":"591390ece2ffcde2310e1275c12971797bd7b9bc","tid":2282473,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T01:46:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">YouTube down: Company says they&rsquo;re working to fix outage</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fox7austin.com/news/youtube-is-down-company-says-theyre-working-to-fix-it\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fox7austin.com%2Fnews%2Fyoutube-is-down-company-says-theyre-working-to-fix-it&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Au4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=263c5bb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fox7austin.com/news/youtube-is-down-company-says-theyre-working-to-fix-it</a>"},{"pid":"98b6aadfac47a8fcad7249e4dc3da66c70514bac","tid":2282473,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T01:48:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">YouTube證實全球大當機 緊急修補中</span></strong><br />\n鉅亨網編譯余曉惠2020/11/12 09:39<br />\n<br />\nTagYouTube影音串流當機Google<br />\n影音平台 YouTube 全球大當機，使用者點選播放鍵無法觀看影片，只會出現發生錯誤，請稍後再試的字樣。YouTube 團隊在推特上證實此事，正在修補中。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">當機問題似乎也影響其他使用 YouTube 基礎架構的服務，包括 YouTube TV、YouTube Music，都無法正常運作。</span><br />\n<br />\n根據 <a href=\"http://DownDetector.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FDownDetector.com&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Au4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=8f912a74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">DownDetector.com</a>， 這次當機影響約 25 萬美國和國際用戶。<br />\n<br />\n這是 Google(GOOGL-US) 旗下知名影音平台 YouTube 今年來至少第二次當機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4542186?exp=a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cnyes.com%2Fnews%2Fid%2F4542186%3Fexp%3Da&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Au4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=e5c1149f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4542186?exp=a</a>"},{"pid":"dda7ea95d1e5a1ae677d574f64a018785fb4d4b6","tid":2282473,"uid":119667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T02:35:48.000Z","msg":"封鎖真相"},{"pid":"0b31267547d1e8ab1f97fafbfdc919149f43cfba","tid":2282473,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T02:42:25.000Z","msg":"洗緊登登D證據同新聞"},{"pid":"2f8ca22dfdc5cc3b6c2b4a488fa641a1d4923882","tid":2282473,"uid":167394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b31267547d1e8ab1f97fafbfdc919149f43cfba","tid":2282473,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T02:42:25.000Z","msg":"洗緊登登D證據同新聞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T02:45:17.000Z","msg":"唔關事 一直洗開<br />\n我估係改AI 先會咁大影響<br />\n拜登<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}